milestones.description: Kapil Dev has broken the record for most ducks (3) in ODIs for IND, going past Srinivas Venkataraghavan's 2
Mark Burgess and Jeremy Coney's 58-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 55 between Vic Pollard and Glenn Turner
Vengsarkar and Sandeep Patil's 92-run partnership is IND's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 76 between Amarnath and Vengsarkar
